316
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:27,939
he can also

317
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:29,790
guide our company's artists.

318
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,690
You are right.

319
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:31,839
I know.

320
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:34,220
