328
00:13:54,970 --> 00:13:55,869
I did it

329
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:58,520
according to the company's
assessment of work ability.

330
00:13:58,740 --> 00:13:59,790
Yang Huiting,

331
00:13:59,900 --> 00:14:02,320
